  <num>7-2045</num>
  <heading>Judicial review.</heading>
  <text>A person aggrieved by a final decision of the Mayor may appeal the decision to the District of Columbia Court of Appeals pursuant to § <cite path="§2-510">2-510</cite>.</text>
